Enum Class ActionRole

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<ActionRole>
org.nasdanika.architecture.core.ActionRole
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<ActionRole>, Constable, org.eclipse.emf.common.util.Enumerator
public enum ActionRole extends Enum<ActionRole> implements org.eclipse.emf.common.util.Enumerator
A representation of the literals of the enumeration 'Action Role', and utility methods for working with them. Action role defines parent's action reference to which to put element's action. In other words, it defines where this element action will be displayed in the generated HTML UI.
